intent.user_query: What is the distribution of sales amounts (e.g., how many sales are between $0-$100, $100-$200, etc.)?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT CASE WHEN TotalAmount BETWEEN 0 AND 100 THEN '0-100' WHEN TotalAmount BETWEEN 101 AND 200 THEN '101-200' ELSE '200+' END AS AmountRange, COUNT(*) FROM fitness_db.Sales GROUP BY 1;

arguments.sql: SELECT CASE WHEN TotalAmount BETWEEN 0 AND 100 THEN '0-100' WHEN TotalAmount BETWEEN 101 AND 200 THEN '101-200' ELSE '200+' END AS AmountRange, COUNT(*) FROM fitness_db.Sales GROUP BY 1;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
